## I am Rocky on do-host1.

## Each heartbeat:
1. POST heartbeat to RCC so dashboard shows rocky online:
   `curl -s -X POST https://api.{{RCC_HOST}}/api/heartbeat/rocky -H "Content-Type: application/json" -H "Authorization: Bearer $RCC_AUTH_TOKEN" -d "{\"status\":\"online\",\"host\":\"do-host1\",\"ts\":\"$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)\"}"`
